# PhotoLib – Project TODO

This document tracks planned work, ideas, and architectural notes.
It is intentionally incomplete and evolves with the project.

---

## Backend – Core API

### Photos

- [x] Separate photo metadata from file endpoints
- [x] Store originals and thumbnails separately
- [x] Add thumbnail endpoint
- [ ] Decide on delete strategy (soft vs hard)
- [ ] Implement soft delete logic (IsDeleted)
- [ ] Handle file cleanup on hard delete (if used)
- [ ] Add metadata-only GET /photo/{id}
- [ ] Add PUT /photo/{id} for updating title & description

### Galleries

- [ ] Review GalleryController endpoints
- [ ] Decide gallery delete behavior
- [ ] Add gallery-level sync support

