## Frontend – Gallery & Photo Viewing

- [x] Gallery grid view (masonry / quilt-style layout)
- [x] Photo viewer mode (single photo focus)
- [x] Next / previous navigation
- [x] Thumbnail carousel in viewer mode
- [ ] Empty gallery state (no photos yet)

### Edit Photo Metadata UX

- [ ] Disable Save button until title or description is changed
- [ ] Detect dirty state by comparing initial vs current values
- [ ] Show subtle visual hint when form has unsaved changes

### Viewer Modes

- [ ] Standard viewer mode (utility-focused, current default)
- [ ] Presentation / postcard viewer mode
  - [ ] Layout: photo on the left
  - [ ] Title below the photo
  - [ ] Description on the right
  - [ ] Visually elegant, non-utility look (illustration / postcard feel)
- [ ] Toggle button to switch between viewer modes
- [ ] Remember last used viewer mode per session

### Fullscreen

- [ ] Fullscreen photo viewing mode
- [ ] Toggle fullscreen on/off from viewer controls
- [ ] Hide non-essential UI in fullscreen mode
- [ ] Restore previous viewer mode after exiting fullscreen

