## Ideas / Notes

- Cloud storage support (Blob / S3) – future version
- Multiple thumbnail sizes
- EXIF parsing on backend
- Distinct UI modes:
  - Gallery overview (grid / masonry)
  - Photo viewer (utility-focused)
  - Photo presentation / postcard mode
  - Fullscreen viewer
  - Overlay windows (properties, full-size)
- Consider enforcing gallery creation only together with first photo upload
